    "When designing interfaces, Data-Copilot generates code for each user request.",
    "It then assesses whether there are similarities among these requests that can be merged or abstracted.",
    "Multiple table tasksMost prompting methods are for a single table task; here, we list several studies that address multiple tasks.",
